    					<marginalia_text>
    						scit&egrave;. Oeconomic&egrave;.
    					</marginalia_text>
    				</position>
    			</language>
    			<translation>
    				Knowingly. Methodically.
    			</translation>
    		</marginalia>
    		<marginalia hand="Italian">
    			<language ident="LA">
    				<position place="intext" book_orientation="0">
    					<marginalia_text>
    						) Peritiss[im]a subtiliss[im]a
    						profundiss[im]a postrem&ograve; etiam potentiss[im]a cuiusq[uam] professionis
    					</marginalia_text>
    					<emphasis method="chalk" type="straight"/>
    				</position>
    				<position place="tail" book_orientation="0">
    					<marginalia_text>
    						puncta, cert&egrave; paucissima. Illa pauca
    						curiosissim&egrave; perscrutanda, et vnic&egrave; multiplicanda.
    					</marginalia_text>
    				</position>
    			</language>
    			<translation>
    				) Certainly, the fewest fragments of any profession are the most expert, the most subtle, the most profound, <!-- 'Punta' possibly used in the Ramist sense. -->
    				and lastly, even the most potent. These few things must be studied most diligently and multiplied to a singular degree.
    			</translation>
    		</marginalia>
        
